description: Most of the 12,000 who fled the fire on the Greek island last week are still sleeping rough.
title: Greece arrests five over Lesbos migrant camp blaze
title_page: Greece arrests five over Lesbos migrant camp blaze - BBC News
maintext: The Greek government's aim is to shelter the 12,000 plus migrants from Moria in the new temporary camp at present, though it acknowledges that most are reluctant to go there. After the squalor of Moria most migrants want to go elsewhere in Europe.
